LayoutNode.Content: Restrictions Maximum weight for Priority Mail International® is 70 lbs. Maximum weight for Priority Mail International Flat Rate Envelopes and Small Flat Rate Priced Boxes is 4 lbs. Maximum weight for medium and large Priority Mail International Flat Rate Boxes is 20 lbs. Some countries have lower weight restrictions. View Country-Specific Restrictions When sealing a Flat Rate Envelope or Box, the container flaps must be able to close within the normal folds. Preparing International Shipments There are restrictions for mailing restricted, prohibited, and hazardous materials, including cigarettes and smokeless tobacco. See All Restrictions
